<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;; font-size:xx-small;">This box: <a href="/wiki/Template:Aqidah" title="Template:Aqidah"><span title="View this template" style="">view</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Aqidah" title="Template talk:Aqidah"><span title="Discussion about this template" style="">talk</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Aqidah&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Aqidah&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";">edit</span></a></div>
</center>
</td>
</tr>
